    %p Bipolar disorder (previously known as Manic Depression) is usually defined in terms of Mental (cognitive) or Affective (mood) cycling. BipolarType adds Physical (caloric) and Financial (monetary) cycles.
  %p.center
    -@realms.each do |realm|
      =link_to realm.symbolic_name, realm_path(realm.path)
  -if @realm.generic?
    %p Note: the moon emoji are not meant to imply that the cycle is exclusively monthly (lunar). The pattern is also present in yearly (seasonal), weekly, daily (circadian), and ultradian cycles. <em>Any</em> recurring life cycle that can be divided into four quarters with a reset or time-out between the fourth and first quarters qualifies.
